Feature: User Registration

  Scenario: Successful registration with all fields
    Given User is on registration form page
    When User enters valid name "John Doe"
    And User enters valid email "john@example.com"
    And User enters valid phone "+1234567890"
    And User submits the registration form
    Then Registration succeeds with HTTP 200
    And User receives success message

  Scenario: Successful registration with required fields only
    Given User is on registration form page
    When User enters valid name "Jane Smith"
    And User enters valid email "jane@example.com"
    And User does not enter phone
    And User submits the registration form
    Then Registration succeeds with HTTP 200

  Scenario: Registration fails with invalid email format
    Given User is on registration form page
    When User enters invalid email "bob.example.com"
    And User submits the registration form
    Then Form validation fails

  Scenario: Registration fails with missing name
    Given User is on registration form page
    When User does not enter name
    And User enters valid email "test@example.com"
    And User submits the registration form
    Then Form validation fails

  Scenario: Registration fails with missing email
    Given User is on registration form page
    When User enters valid name "Alice Brown"
    And User does not enter email
    And User submits the registration form
    Then API returns 400 error